getPSDELogicNodes.name: 删除置顶
getPSDELogicNodes.sql: delete from T_IBZ_TOP  where type = 'product' and objectid = ? and account = ?

getPSDELogicNodes.name: 获取置顶最大排序值
getPSDELogicNodes.sql: select (case when max(t1.`objectorder`) >= 16000000  then max(t1.`objectorder`) + 1 else 16000000 end) as `objectorder` from T_IBZ_TOP t1 where t1.type = 'product' and t1.account= ?

getAllPSAppDELogics.logicName: 项目任务快速分组计数器
getAllPSAppDELogics.name: 项目任务快速分组计数器

getPSDELogicNodes.name: 进行中的任务
getPSDELogicNodes.sql:
select count(t.id) as YSTARTASKCNT from zt_task t where t.deleted = '0' and t.`status` = 'doing' and t.project = ?
and t.parent <= '0'

getPSDELogicNodes.name: 未关闭的任务数
getPSDELogicNodes.sql: select count(t.id) as UNCOMPLETETASKCNT from zt_task t where t.deleted = '0' and t.`status` in( 'wait','cancel','doing') and t.project = ? and t.parent <= '0'

getPSDELogicNodes.name: 未关闭任务数
getPSDELogicNodes.sql: select count(t.id) as UNCLOSETASKCNT from zt_task t where t.deleted = '0' and t.`status` <> 'closed' and t.project = ? and t.parent <= '0'

getPSDELogicNodes.name: 已关闭的任务数
getPSDELogicNodes.sql: select count(t.id) as CLOSETASKCNT from zt_task t where t.deleted = '0' and t.`status` = 'closed' and t.project = ? and t.parent <= '0'

getPSDELogicNodes.name: 指派给我的任务数
getPSDELogicNodes.sql: select count(t.id) as ASSTOMYTASKCNT from zt_task t where t.deleted = '0' and t.assignedTo = ? and t.project = ? and t.parent <= '0'

getPSDELogicNodes.name: 所有任务
getPSDELogicNodes.sql: select count(t.id) as ALLTASKCNT from zt_task t where t.deleted = '0'  and t.project = ? and t.parent <= '0'

getPSDELogicNodes.name: 已完成的任务数
getPSDELogicNodes.sql: select count(t.id) as YCOMPLETETASKCNT from zt_task t where t.deleted = '0' and t.`status` = 'done' and t.project = ? and t.parent <= '0'

getPSDELogicNodes.name: 已取消任务
getPSDELogicNodes.sql: select count(t.id) as CANCELTASKCNT from zt_task t where t.deleted = '0' and t.`status` = 'cancel' and t.project = ? and t.parent <= '0'

getPSDELogicNodes.name: 未开始的任务数
getPSDELogicNodes.sql: select count(t.id) as UNSTARTTASKCNT from zt_task t where t.deleted = '0' and t.`status` = 'wait' and t.project = ? and t.parent <= '0'

getPSDELogicNodes.name: 我完成的任务数
getPSDELogicNodes.sql: select count(t.id) as MYCOMPLETETASKCNT from zt_task t where t.deleted = '0' and t.`finishedby` = ? and t.project = ? and t.parent <= '0'

getPSDELogicNodes.name: 需求变更数
getPSDELogicNodes.sql: select count(t.id) as STORYCHANGECNT from zt_task t left join zt_story t21 on t.story = t21.id where t.deleted = '0'  and t.project = ? and t.storyVersion < t21.version and t21.`status` <> 'changed' and t.parent <= '0'
